OL,6,F"We want to remind people that
OL,7,Fcriminal proceedings against Axel
OL,8,FRudakubana are active and therefore it
OL,9,Fis extremely important that there is
OL,10,Fno reporting, commentary or sharing of
OL,11,Finformation online which could in any
OL,12,Fway prejudice these proceedings.
OL,14,F"We are determined to deliver justice
OL,15,Fin this case."
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, Home Secretary Yvette
OL,18,FCooper also warned against public
OL,19,Fspeculation over the case.
